Correctamundo Scott.

The muffler Guru that's manufacturing the stainless muffler's I sell for
the Vanagon's told me that stainless flange plates would have to be a
minimum of 1" to avoid warping.

I can't see adding 1" plate just for the sake of not surface rusting.




